    "summary": "Key Agents is the hub that makes the main N1Hub agent architecture explicit. It gathers the Personal AI Assistant, DeepMine mining workers, planning agents, N-Infinity maintenance roles, and review or validation roles into one graph-visible cluster. The hub matters because the project is no longer powered by a single generic assistant; it is becoming a routed system of specialized intelligence surfaces. By naming the cluster, the vault makes ownership, delegation, and future implementation much easier to reason about.",
